   "type": "text",
   "x": 40,
   "y": 372,
   "width": 1660.43,
   "height": 15,
   "text": "One shared proxy network lets NPM reach the upstream containers by name without exposing their HTTP ports to the LAN. A wildcard certificate comes from Let's Encrypt over a Cloudflare DNS-01 challenge, then Force SSL and HTTP/2 go on the published host.",
   "originalText": "One shared proxy network lets NPM reach the upstream containers by name without exposing their HTTP ports to the LAN. A wildcard certificate comes from Let's Encrypt over a Cloudflare DNS-01 challenge, then Force SSL and HTTP/2 go on the published host.",
